          Add a date
        </h2>
        <p
          class="mint-body-large text-base-dark margin-top-0 margin-bottom-2"
        >
          Add a custom date or date range to your model timeline.
        </p>
        <div>
          <button
            class="usa-button usa-button usa-button--unstyled"
            data-testid="button"
            type="button"
          >
            <svg
